                                    </div>

                                    <div class="next-step-card">
                                        <div class="step-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h4>Explore the API</h4>
                                        <p>Learn about the REST API and start building integrations.</p>
                                        <a href="/docs/api" class="btn btn-outline">API Reference</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Troubleshooting -->
                            <div class="troubleshooting-section">
                                <h3>Common Issues</h3>
                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>Port already in use</h4>
                                    <p>If port 3000 is already in use, change the <code>PORT</code> value in your <code>.env</code> file to a different port number.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>Database initialization fails</h4>
                                    <p>Make sure you have write permissions in the project directory. The database file will be created in <code>database/sayonika.db</code>.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>Module not found errors</h4>
                                    <p>Run <code>npm install</code> again to ensure all dependencies are properly installed.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-link">
                                    <p>
                                        Need more help? Check our <a href="/docs/troubleshooting">troubleshooting guide</a> or
                                        <a href="https://github.com/Dynamicaaa/Sayonika/issues" target="_blank">create an issue</a> on GitHub.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
